cat(
  '<div class="note-box">',
  '<p><strong>Direction mistakes.</strong> Correlation sign errors are more common than slope sign errors. ',
  'For correlation, <strong>', corr_sign_best$group, '</strong> has the lowest sign-error rate (', fmt_pct(corr_sign_best$sign_error_rate_numeric, accuracy = 0.1), '). ',
  'For slope, sign errors are low across all conditions, so I would keep this as a descriptive check rather than a main outcome.</p>',
